Olkuaak lolkiristianoi


1  Ntadamu ninche metaa ilooning'isho too laitoriak nening'isho, neas pooki siaai metii esunkureisho, 
2  nememor likae tung'ani, nepaash olarrabal, neaku loobor, neitoduaaya esupatisho too ltung'ana pooki. 
3  Amu eikira sii apa iyiook ilmoda, nikigolong'u, neitapong'oyioki iyiook, nikiaaku rrindiki loo ng'uarrat o sikarri oo mpukunot pooki, nikinturraa nkolong'i ang te ntorroni o lom, neibayuni iyiook iltung'ana nikimbayuno iyiook maate; 
4  kake ore ake pee eliooyu esidano oe enyorrata e supatisho e Enkai Olaitajeunoni lang, 
5  neitajeu ninye iyiook neme te nkaraki nkiasin nikitaasa iyiook ti atua esupatisho, kake te nkaraki olng'ur lenye, te nkitukuoto o enkitang'ejukoto o einoto ti atua Enkiyang'et Sinyati, 
6  ina natubukoko ninye iyiook te nkiputakinoto ti atua Yesu Kristo Olaitajeunoni lang, 
7  pee eikenaki iyiook esupatisho te mpiris enye nikiaaku ilajung'ok to siligi le nkishui oo ntarasi. Ororei osipa ele.


8  Ayieu naa nimbung akurraki kuna baa, peyie aa ore looiruko Enkai nejurru aaitayiolo ate nkiasin sidain; kuna ninche sidain naata dupoto too ltung'ana. 
9  Kake tapaasha nchankarri, iishoritin oo lmakui, impaashat o enchankar oo mbaa oo nkitanapat, amu meeta eretoto naa pesho. 
10  Ore oltung'ani okepari, indipa aikoo ninye ene dukuya o eniare, talama. 
11  Iyiolo ajo ore oltung'ani oikununo inji netapong'ori naa aing'okoni netudung'oko kewan enkiguana.


12   Te nairriu nanu Atemas aashu Tikikos meeu enitii, tonyuaa oleng, wou ene natii te Nikapolis, amu atudung'o pee aton te ine te nkata e nkirobi. 
13   Tonyuaa isosionie Senos, ilo loo nkitanapat o Apolos te lototo enye; nimincho eng'oriki hoo toki. 
14  Naa nchoo iltung'ana lang meitamoo ate nkiasin sidain, pee eretu nkolati naarrish nemeaku ilemeeta ilng'anayio.


15  Eirriwaki intae enkirorokino kulo pooki laboitare. Iroroki lelo pooki oonyor iyiook ti atua enkirukoto.

Metaa empiris te nebo intae pooki.

